F Strings
If i dont want to do typecasting all the time then it is very useful.
Example:
age = int(input("What is your age: "))
print(f"My age is {age}.")

To make the things write next to each other:
print(i, end= " ")

listede range kullanirken 2ser 2ser atlatmak böyle yaziliyor:
for i in range(0,10,2):
    print(i, end= " ")
